#### Blocks

Blocks can be set with:

```js
{% raw %}
{% block blockName %}
  HTML Here
{% endblock %}
{% endraw %}
```

To change the components that are included by default, set their equivalent blocks, for example:

```js
{% raw %}
{% block header %}
  {{ header({
    homepageUrl: "/custom-url"
  }) }}
{% endblock %}
{% endraw %}
```

